        <li>Uses <a href="https://matthiasott.com/notes/how-i-structure-my-css" rel="nofollow">my own opinionated CSS/Sass structure</a></li>
        <li>Example implementation of a web font loading strategy (<a href="https://www.zachleat.com/web/comprehensive-webfonts/#critical-foft-preload" rel="nofollow">critical FOFT with preload</a>)</li>
        <li>Basic fluid typography based on <a href="https://utopia.fyi" rel="nofollow">Utopia</a></li>
        <li>Basic dark mode support (using <code>prefers-color-scheme</code> and CSS Custom Properties)</li>
        <li>RSS feed 🧡</li>
        <li>XML sitemap</li>
